t\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\"}, {\"begin\": 1126, \"end\": 1145, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tanni_Grey-Thompson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tanni Grey-Thompson\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tanni_Grey-Thompson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tanni_Grey-Thompson\"}, {\"begin\": 1215, \"end\": 1226, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999999899030172, \"rank\": 9.684216116152328e-09, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"four Paralympic golds\", \"from\": 1038, \"to\": 1059}, {\"ngram\": \"ambitions\", \"from\": 1189, \"to\": 1198}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She told the PA news agency: \\\"Obviously the question always comes: is this going to be your last one?\", \"from\": 1237, \"to\": 1338, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the PA news agency\", \"from\": 1246, \"to\": 1264}, {\"ngram\": \"the question\", \"from\": 1277, \"to\": 1289}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am 32 and that's kind of the age we see a lot of women dropping out of our sport.\", \"from\": 1339, \"to\": 1422, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"kind of the age\", \"from\": 1358, \"to\": 1373}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1381, \"to\": 1386}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 1390, \"to\": 1395}, {\"ngram\": \"our sport\", \"from\": 1412, \"to\": 1421}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I feel like I am going to have a lot of decisions to make next cycle but I'd like to make it to LA.\", \"from\": 1424, \"to\": 1524, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1456, \"to\": 1461}, {\"ngram\": \"decisions\", \"from\": 1465, \"to\": 1474}, {\"ngram\": \"next cycle\", \"from\": 1483, \"to\": 1493}, {\"ngram\": \"LA\", \"from\": 1521, \"to\": 1523}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I'd like to see how many more Games are in me.\", \"from\": 1525, \"to\": 1571, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"how many more Games\", \"from\": 1541, \"to\": 1560}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am still getting quicker, I am still getting stronger, everything's still going in the right direction, so there is no reason for me to step out now.\", \"from\": 1573, \"to\": 1725, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 1631, \"to\": 1641}, {\"ngram\": \"the right direction\", \"from\": 1659, \"to\": 1678}, {\"ngram\": \"no reason\", \"from\": 1692, \"to\": 1701}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is not a single thought in my head that this could be the last - unless something goes terribly wrong.\\\"\", \"from\": 1727, \"to\": 1837, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a single thought\", \"from\": 1741, \"to\": 1757}, {\"ngram\": \"my head\", \"from\": 1761, \"to\": 1768}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 1806, \"to\": 1815}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yorkshire-born Cockroft made a statement of intent in May by winning the 15th and 16th world titles of her glittering career in Kobe, Japan.\", \"from\": 1839, \"to\": 1979, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1854, \"end\": 1862, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Don_Cockroft\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Cockroft\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q14128148\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Don_Cockroft\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Don_Cockroft\"}, {\"begin\": 1967, \"end\": 1971, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kobe\", \"score\": 0.999999402985346, \"rank\": 5.970057629081287e-07, \"text\": \"Kobe\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kobe\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kobe\"}, {\"begin\": 1973, \"end\": 1978, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"score\": 0.9647388616150574, \"rank\": 0.03651732126174863, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a statement\", \"from\": 1868, \"to\": 1879}, {\"ngram\": \"intent\", \"from\": 1883, \"to\": 1889}, {\"ngram\": \"May\", \"from\": 1893, \"to\": 1896}, {\"ngram\": \"the 15th and 16th world titles\", \"from\": 1908, \"to\": 1938}, {\"ngram\": \"her glittering career\", \"from\": 1942, \"to\": 1963}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yet, given her sustained supremacy, she is \\\"hyper-aware\\\" of the pressure on her shoulders.\", \"from\": 1981, \"to\": 2071, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her sustained supremacy\", \"from\": 1992, \"to\": 2015}, {\"ngram\": \"the pressure\", \"from\": 2041, \"to\": 2053}, {\"ngram\": \"her shoulders\", \"from\": 2057, \"to\": 2070}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I one hundred per cent think I am the one to beat, in the least big-headed way,\\\" said Cockroft.\", \"from\": 2073, \"to\": 2169, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2160, \"end\": 2168, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Don_Cockroft\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Cockroft\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q14128148\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Don_Cockroft\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Don_Cockroft\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"one hundred per cent\", \"from\": 2076, \"to\": 2096}, {\"ngram\": \"the least big-headed way\", \"from\": 2128, \"to\": 2152}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am number one in the world, I have retained that title since 2018.\", \"from\": 2171, \"to\": 2240, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"number\", \"from\": 2177, \"to\": 2183}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 2191, \"to\": 2200}, {\"ngram\": \"that title\", \"from\": 2218, \"to\": 2228}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And it's scary; I am so hyper-aware of the fact the target's on my back.\", \"from\": 2241, \"to\": 2313, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the fact\", \"from\": 2280, \"to\": 2288}, {\"ngram\": \"the target\", \"from\": 2289, \"to\": 2299}, {\"ngram\": \"my back\", \"from\": 2305, \"to\": 2312}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But that's what keeps me going.\", \"from\": 2315, \"to\": 2347, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am never satisfied, I am never happy with any race that's not a fast time.\", \"from\": 2348, \"to\": 2424, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any race\", \"from\": 2392, \"to\": 2400}, {\"ngram\": \"a fast time\", \"from\": 2412, \"to\": 2423}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am always asking questions and I think the minute you stop and are satisfied with the performance you have laid down it's probably the day I am going to have to retire.\\\"\", \"from\": 2426, \"to\": 2598, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"questions\", \"from\": 2446, \"to\": 2455}, {\"ngram\": \"the minute\", \"from\": 2468, \"to\": 2478}, {\"ngram\": \"the performance\", \"from\": 2511, \"to\": 2526}, {\"ngram\": \"the day\", \"from\": 2560, \"to\": 2567}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Emerging Chinese athlete Hanyu Lan finished runner-up to Cockroft in both the 100m and 800m at the recent world championships.\", \"from\": 2600, \"to\": 2726, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2625, \"end\": 2630, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yuzuru_Hanyu\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2636733322192348e-25, \"text\": \"Hanyu\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13219587\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yuzuru_Hanyu\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yuzuru_Hanyu\"}, {\"begin\": 2657, \"end\": 2665, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Don_Cockroft\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Cockroft\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q190